descriptionHtml:
Mello FM is the only radio station transmitting from the city of Montego Bay. When it was created in 2004 it covered only Western Jamaica, but in 2010 it began broadcasting islandwide. Its contents are mostly music.

Listen to your favourite radio stations from Jamaica in one place no matter where you are you only need your android device.

Now you get to enjoy your radios from Jamaica anywhere in the world. Jamaican beats anywhere where you have an internet connection .

With Jamaican Radio App, you can find the widest range of FM, AM and online radios of the island.

With our app, you can choose your favourite Radio stations and access them easily.
